OL,3,COver-the-counter nasal sprays may keep
OL,4,Ccoughs, colds and flu at bay, trial
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe benefits were greater for those
OL,8,Fwho used the sprays around six times a
OL,9,Fday, the researchers from the
OL,10,FUniversity of Southampton said.
OL,12,FPeople using nasal sprays were also
OL,13,Fless likely to be prescribed
OL,14,Fantibiotics compared to those
OL,15,Freceiving the usual standard care,
OL,16,Fthey added.
OL,18,FThe team said its findings could offer
OL,19,Fa cheap and easy way to stop people
OL,20,Ffrom falling severely ill with
OL,21,Frespiratory infections.
