OL,3,COver-the-counter nasal sprays may keep
OL,4,Ccoughs, colds and flu at bay, trial
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FFor the study, which was funded by the
OL,8,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,9,FResearch (NIHR) and published in the
OL,10,Fjournal The Lancet Respiratory
OL,11,FMedicine, the researchers recruited
OL,12,F13,799 patients from 332 GP surgeries.
OL,14,FAll patients either had an existing
OL,15,Fhealth problem, had respiratory
OL,16,Finfections in the past, or were at
OL,17,Fhigh risk of infection.
