OL,3,COver-the-counter nasal sprays may keep
OL,4,Ccoughs, colds and flu at bay, trial
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FPatients were randomly assigned to
OL,8,Freceive either a Vicks-First-Defence
OL,9,Fgel-based nasal spray, a saline liquid-
OL,10,Fbased nasal spray, or an online
OL,11,Fresource that helps people with
OL,12,Frespiratory illnesses with exercise
OL,13,Fand stress levels.
OL,15,FCompared to the usual standard care,
OL,16,Fwhich involved getting NHS advice on
OL,17,Fhow to manage respiratory illnesses,
OL,18,Fthe sprays cut the number of days
OL,19,Ftaken off work or other activities by
OL,20,Fup to 30%, the researchers said.
