OL,4,Ccoughs, colds and flu at bay, trial
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FMeanwhile, stress management and
OL,8,Fexercise online advice reduced the
OL,9,Fincidence of infections by a modest
OL,10,F5%, the team added.
OL,12,FProf Little said: "Our results show
OL,13,Fnasal sprays work well to reduce the
OL,14,Fduration and severity of respiratory
OL,15,Finfections, and the interference with
OL,16,Fnormal activities, which is
OL,17,Fparticularly important in light of the
OL,18,Fwinter infection surge the UK
OL,19,Fregularly experiences.
